PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775747465
OL,3,CVictims and bereaved families given
OL,4,Cmore time to challenge sentences
OL,6,FShe said: "I am delighted that, after
OL,7,Fyears of campaigning led by Tracey
OL,8,FHanson following the tragic death of
OL,9,Fher son Josh, and supported by
OL,10,Fbereaved families, the government has
OL,11,Ffinally listened.
OL,13,F"I have long supported and worked
OL,14,Fclosely with Tracey on her campaign
OL,15,Fsince 2019, following the appalling
OL,16,Finjustice she experienced, and I hope
OL,17,Fthis marks an important step towards
OL,18,Fgreater parity between victims and
OL,19,Foffenders."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
