PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775747465
OL,3,CVictims and bereaved families given
OL,4,Cmore time to challenge sentences
OL,6,FJosh Hanson was murdered in an
OL,7,Funprovoked knife attack in a bar in
OL,8,FHillingdon, west London in 2015 and
OL,9,Fhis mother set up The Josh Hanson
OL,10,FTrust in his name.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FJustice Secretary David Lammy said
OL,18,Fvictims and their families need "time
OL,19,Fto breathe" and get advice after a
OL,20,Fsentence is handed down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775747465
OL,3,CVictims and bereaved families given
OL,4,Cmore time to challenge sentences
OL,6,F"This change means they'll have more
OL,7,Ftime to do this ` and most
OL,8,Fimportantly, get the justice they
OL,9,Fdeserve," he added.
OL,11,FThe Conservatives claimed the
OL,12,Fgovernment's move represented a U-turn.
OL,14,FShadow justice minister Kieran Mullan
OL,15,Fsaid: "After months and months of
OL,16,Fvoting down sensible proposals for
OL,17,Freform this is a step forward and
OL,18,Freflects the strength of feeling from
OL,19,Fvictims, families and campaigners who
OL,20,Fhave been calling for change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
